Little River sunset



After dinner, we took a romantic moonlight walk (the near-full moon was just rising) on Little River Beach.
The remains of the sunset were still lighting up the sky.
Taken Tuesday, July 03, 2001, 09:00:10pm.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 994kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/30s @ F2.8, ISO 100, 38mm
